      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained over the years. The engine is strong and reliable, and the transmission shifts smoothly, ensuring a dependable driving experience for its next owner. The interior is clean and has been well-cared for, though you may find some minor cosmetic wear and small exterior stone chips consistent with regular use. It has a clean service history and is ready for the road without any immediate repairs needed.",
