    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54B32 power plant remains in peak operating condition, delivering a razor-sharp throttle response via its six individual throttle bodies. This example features a reinforced rear subframe and recently serviced rod bearings, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission engages with mechanical precision, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Suspension kinematics remain factory-spec, providing the communicative feedback and neutral handling balance this chassis is renowned for. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the discerning collector seeking mechanical purity.",
      "price": 48500.0,
