      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior finish is flawless, featuring deep, mirror-like paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are no stone chips, door dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition, retaining that new-car scent with absolutely no wear on the leather bolsters or carpets. Every switch and electronic feature operates exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a complete folder of service records and recent preventative maintenance. It comes complete with all original keys, factory manuals, and a custom fit-cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key, investment-quality example.",
      "price": 43900.0,
